00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.285
Orchestration tools are used for automating deployment,

00:00:03.285 --> 00:00:07.005
scaling, and managing your containerized applications.

00:00:07.004 --> 00:00:10.275
Amazon ECS or Elastic Container Service

00:00:10.275 --> 00:00:13.919
is a container orchestration service that supports Docker,

00:00:13.919 --> 00:00:16.545
assisting with managing your containers.

00:00:16.545 --> 00:00:18.780
There are several useful features,

00:00:18.780 --> 00:00:22.605
including launching and stopping Docker containers,

00:00:22.605 --> 00:00:27.644
scaling your applications, querying the state of your applications, etc.

00:00:27.644 --> 00:00:30.390
It is really a convenience type service to

00:00:30.390 --> 00:00:34.600
assist you with the administration of your Docker containers.

